Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.76,0:00:05.48,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The plan takes all contingencies into account.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.19,0:00:09.98,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Everything is set to make it look like an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.81,0:00:14.49,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I've already prepared the poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.23,0:00:19.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Soon we'll find out whether his blood is as red as ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.46,0:00:23.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fortunately for us, the museum will be closed next Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.68,0:00:27.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No staff members beside us will be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.71,0:00:29.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.19,0:00:31.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should get this over with as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, Seikanji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.26,0:00:38.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{You're in a hurry since the deadline for repaying your loan is approaching, right?}You're in a hurry since you have to repay your loan soon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.69,0:00:39.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.76,0:00:43.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're going to bring that up, I should remind you the manager's embezzlement has been found out,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.73,0:00:46.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and he'll be fired at the end of the month.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.27,0:00:51.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're one to talk, given your heavy losses from investing in worthless shares.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.50,0:00:53.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess it's just me then.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.70,0:00:56.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm the only one who isn't in a hurry to get this over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.16,0:00:59.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.83,0:01:07.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We all know you're anxious that he could strike you from his will any day, being his ex.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.08,0:01:12.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now. Quarrelling will get us nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.30,0:01:15.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We only have one common goal:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.96,0:01:20.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The death of Jisaburō Izumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.55,0:01:24.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why we have gathered here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.97,0:01:28.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moyono{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, let me confirm once more:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.92,0:01:37.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should we be successful in killing Jisaburō, you'll divide half of the fortune that you inherit between us three.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:45.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The person who kills him receives 80%, and the other two receive 10% each to keep quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.65,0:01:51.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somehow it seems that I'm the only one losing out here, but I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.41,0:01:57.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I try it on my own and end up being exposed, I'll lose everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.65,0:02:01.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if we work together, we'll have a better chance for success.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.36,0:02:07.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Very well. Then we'll carry out the plan next Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.81,0:02:24.94,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Seeking comprehensive answers, he clears all mysteries and codes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.94,0:02:26.99,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A dangerous conversation in the Noh mask museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.99,0:02:29.20,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What secrets do their three masks hide?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.20,0:02:30.95,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.95,0:02:32.65,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.65,0:02:35.54,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.10,0:04:31.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this? Looks like they're closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.17,0:04:33.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.43,0:04:36.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter. We have urgent business after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.62,0:04:39.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.81,0:04:42.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd like to see the curator please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.40,0:04:44.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.15,0:04:49.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The museum is closed today, so the curator is not available.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.00,0:04:52.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me! I'm Naruya Akaza.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.53,0:04:55.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have an appointment with Izumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.22,0:05:04.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Moyono Mibu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, right? Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:09.82,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Let me open the front door.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.44,0:05:09.82,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Moyono Mibu (38)\NNoh Mask Museum Accountant and Receptionist
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.88,0:05:21.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Sir, you can't just walk in!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.74,0:05:25.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I just informed you, we're closed today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.58,0:05:31.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, please don't mind me. I've come here to see the curator on urgent business.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:33.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The curator?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.08,0:05:34.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Urgent business?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.09,0:05:38.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I received this letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.59,0:05:43.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saying that Mr. Jisaburō Izumi's life is in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.88,0:05:53.39,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}'Mr. Jisaburō Izumi's life is in danger.'
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.39,0:05:57.63,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}'The culprit will likely make his move soon.'
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.63,0:06:01.19,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}'I will await your arrival, Great Detective Mouri.'
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:03.45,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And there's no name given for the sender.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:05.89,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What will you do, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:09.60,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This Izumi guy's rich, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.60,0:06:12.95,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If you were to protect him, maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.95,0:06:15.18,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}All right! Let's go, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.18,0:06:19.59,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If I ignored a letter like that, it'd blemish my reputation as a great detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.05,0:06:23.99,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Geez, we don't even know whether the letter's for real or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:27.74,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Actually, I just wanted to go see the Noh masks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.44,0:06:33.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so I decided to come and investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.40,0:06:35.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.64,0:06:39.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I probably should have said earlier. Here's my card.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.91,0:06:45.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the great detective, Sleeping Kogorō?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.91,0:06:49.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, people call me that, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.46,0:06:59.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm an old acquaintance of Izumi's.{uso: removed -san, actually is the word "curator" earlier}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.34,0:07:03.59,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,But I'm surprised that you'd bring a kid along when investigating a murder threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.59,0:07:03.59,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Naruya Akaza (40)\NAcquaintance of Jisaburō's / Promoter
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:07.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, the kid really wanted to see the Noh masks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:08.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.62,0:07:11.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your daughter has very refined tastes, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.86,0:07:13.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.39,0:07:18.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How on earth did that leak out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.11,0:07:27.29,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Seinosuke Nagata (60)\NNoh Mask Museum Manager
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.11,0:07:27.29,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Tatsurō Seikanji (45)\NNoh Mask Museum Executive
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.77,0:07:22.67,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Who'd have thought a great detective like him would come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:25.30,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It might be better to put our plan on hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.11,0:07:27.66,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Where is the curator?{uso: "curator" was "Izumi-san"}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.64,0:07:31.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just about time for his visit to the mansion god.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.92,0:07:34.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why Akaza's leading them there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:39.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It's too late to stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.20,0:07:43.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you put a trap there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.80,0:07:45.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:52.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the mansion god?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.67,0:07:58.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There has been a shrine to his ancestors in the northwest of the grounds since ancient times.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.09,0:08:03.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is Mr. Izumi{uso: was "Izumi-san", audio, "Izumi-shi"} a very religious person?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.11,0:08:09.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, a lot of people resent him, so he certainly has a good reason to pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:12.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, there he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.87,0:08:16.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Curator Izumi{uso: -san mistake for -kanchou AGAIN}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.46,0:08:20.92,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Jisaburō Izumi (65)\NNoh Mask Museum Owner
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:20.28,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Akaza{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}. Right on time, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.14,0:08:28.10,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Hatsuho Toba (28)\NJisaburō's Assigned Nurse
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.10,0:08:32.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And? Who would you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:45.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm used to threatening letters, you know. No need to fuss about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.28,0:08:49.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sender went out of their way to send it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.53,0:08:52.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's just an empty threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.97,0:09:08.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.02,0:09:12.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:50.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it hadn't been for these kids, I would have been crushed by that lumber.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.89,0:09:53.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go get me another wheelchair!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.70,0:09:56.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes! I'll do it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.91,0:09:59.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.01,0:10:00.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you waiting for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.31,0:10:02.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.53,0:10:14.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn! Lucky old geezer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.04,0:10:22.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't let my guard down around anyone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:28.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I think I can trust the boy who saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.92,0:10:31.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the young lady as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.93,0:10:38.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mister, you never know what may happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:40.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you should take precautions, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.55,0:10:43.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.09,0:10:45.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what kind of precautions?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.36,0:10:48.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For example, what's exhibited over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.26,0:10:55.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Medals and {\i1}odoshi{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.10,0:10:58.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're plaited cords, arranged in belt form and used as decoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.58,0:11:00.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Odoshi{\i0} are a part of traditional armour.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.96,0:11:03.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then they're probably very sturdy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.75,0:11:06.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:09.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that a wasp? It's rather big!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.51,0:11:11.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's going to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.84,0:11:13.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't exaggerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.80,0:11:15.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it —\hit's a hornet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.91,0:11:18.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Curator Izumi's already been stung once.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.55,0:11:22.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, no! He could die from anaphylactic shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.23,0:11:26.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.13,0:11:36.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why, you! How about this? And this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:40.50,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hey, that's my jacket...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:49.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think about my cherished collection, Mr. Sleeping Kogorō?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.38,0:11:53.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, the masks really are splendid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.63,0:11:55.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do they fit me too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.18,0:12:04.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The museum staff usually wear masks to enhance the atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.33,0:12:10.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're called {\i1}kuwaemen{\i0}. You can wear one just by holding onto this protrusion here with your teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.38,0:12:13.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though of course, you can't talk while wearing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.00,0:12:18.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why the curator says they help preserve a quiet atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.41,0:12:23.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The creator of these masks was a friend of mine, Kodō Matsumoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.50,0:12:26.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He got married a number of times...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.57,0:12:30.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But in the end I was the one who looked after him until he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.42,0:12:34.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because you have an eye for artists.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.05,0:12:39.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a result, I was given the opportunity to exhibit his works posthumously.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.93,0:12:45.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With that accident happening and the hornets flying around, it seems like that letter was telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.57,0:12:58.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This museum was originally a mansion built during my grandfather's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:04.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only thing that remains from that time is the mansion's heart, this fireplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.96,0:13:08.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This place is called the {\i1}yokoza{\i0}, it's where the master of the house would sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.90,0:13:11.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you know that, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.88,0:13:13.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:15.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's still raw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.98,0:13:20.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Under the glow of the fire, the whole family would amuse themselves with stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.42,0:13:23.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.42,0:13:23.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}白い
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.42,0:13:23.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And look! In the light of the fire the mask looks white, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:28.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}面白い
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:28.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The word 'omoshiroi', meaning 'interesting', evolved from that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.36,0:13:30.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's {\i1}interesting.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:39.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There used to be a lattice up there known as a fire rack, to which the pot-hook was fastened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.20,0:13:41.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's gone now because it got in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.11,0:13:48.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That wooden fish is a charm to keep the fire in check, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:18.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn! Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.71,0:14:27.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that chestnut popped out just then!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.65,0:14:31.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've all gone and failed, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.74,0:14:33.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let round two begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.46,0:14:41.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.35,0:14:46.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I ordered some catering as thanks for saving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.52,0:14:49.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Very kind of you. I accept!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.36,0:14:53.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't care about you. The kids are the ones who saved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.26,0:14:59.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've brought a little something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.19,0:15:03.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Washed-rind cheese from Burgundy.{uso: that is a correct term, some of the kinds I buy fall into that category.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:06.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You just returned from France, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.33,0:15:08.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then should I open some wine as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.94,0:15:15.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:22.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{It smells so strongly that they call it\Nthe smell of god's feet.}The smell's so strong that some people call it 'the smell of God's feet'.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.22,0:15:25.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if you give it a try, it has a rich, milky flavour.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.38,0:15:29.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You usually just scoop some up with\Na spoon and eat it as-is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.35,0:15:34.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Executive and manager, come and join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.68,0:15:36.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, we couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:42.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or are you confessing to being the culprit behind those three pranks?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.07,0:15:44.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.38,0:15:46.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, if you insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.46,0:15:50.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, come, come. Sit wherever you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.93,0:15:54.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since if we all eat together, I'll know it's not poisoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:57.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hatsuho, will you be so good as to taste it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:15:58.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:10.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:15.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I should hope so. What do you think, Akaza{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:18.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which of these two white wines would fit better?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.34,0:16:21.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd have to know what it tastes like first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.46,0:16:23.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then take a spoonful, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.53,0:16:25.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.60,0:16:35.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a truly profound taste that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.91,0:16:56.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This scent clearly shows he was poisoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:16:58.76,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.76,0:17:00.28,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who put poison in there, and when?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:06.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nobody move!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.72,0:17:09.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you going, Mr. Executive?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.52,0:17:13.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, well, to call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.54,0:17:18.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll take care of that, so please stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:19.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.05,0:17:19.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.47,0:17:23.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't touch the cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:28.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, I can't reach them. Seems like we're out of range here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.28,0:17:33.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a phone in the kitchen over there. I'll go make the call.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.33,0:17:37.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then tell Inspector Megure from Police HQ that Kogorō Mouri asked you to call.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.38,0:17:38.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.05,0:17:44.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello? Is this the police? One of our guests has been poisoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.65,0:17:46.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please come quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.80,0:17:51.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if they race here it will take the police 20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.95,0:17:56.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do I have to stay covered in cheese in the meantime?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.04,0:17:58.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.69,0:17:59.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Toba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.88,0:18:01.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.45,0:18:04.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please clean just his immediate surroundings and leave the rest as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.90,0:18:06.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.14,0:18:08.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They'll be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.77,0:18:10.46,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Moyono Mibu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.46,0:18:13.14,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She couldn't have put in the poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.57,0:18:16.65,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Executive Seikanji and Manager Nagata...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:19.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Those two didn't get close to the cheese either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.83,0:18:26.14,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And either way, Toba{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} tried the cheese first, so there was no poison in it at that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.14,0:18:27.89,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Was it put in afterwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.89,0:18:31.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No, no one had the chance to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.08,0:18:38.42,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Which means that maybe the poison wasn't in the cheese, but on the butter knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.94,0:18:42.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, where did you get this butter knife from?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.58,0:18:45.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was one on everyone's bread plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.70,0:18:52.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And without knowing who would sit where, it would be impossible to target someone specifically.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.54,0:19:00.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Hey, kid, we're moving somewhere else!}Hey, kid, we're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.77,0:19:06.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.64,0:19:09.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you think so, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:12.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Absolutely!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.77,0:19:16.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please be patient until the police arrive, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:19.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran! Where's the brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:22.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this? I thought he was over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.57,0:19:27.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm getting some coffee for the curator,{not named, certainly no -san -uso.} so I'll look for the boy as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.40,0:19:29.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.93,0:19:37.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That call to the police earlier was a bit weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.50,0:19:41.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wait, isn't this an internal phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.71,0:19:46.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You in there, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.83,0:19:47.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.31,0:19:50.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.68,0:19:54.33,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:00.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.70,0:20:08.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouse! There's a mouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:14.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did the coffee spill?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.00,0:20:15.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.01,0:20:20.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, the curator's wondering when the coffee will be ready.{well, there IS a -san this time, but no Izumi =p -uso.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.35,0:20:22.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:23.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll help!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.77,0:20:25.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.40,0:20:31.91,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This time she didn't have a chance to slip any poison in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.91,0:20:39.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So there was a motive for killing Akaza{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.55,0:20:45.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He flattered me a lot, but apparently he was a vicious businessman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.04,0:20:46.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse my tardiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.44,0:20:51.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want to die like Akaza.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.18,0:20:53.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please stop joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.72,0:20:55.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.32,0:21:00.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one would be foolish enough to try to poison you when the police are on their way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.01,0:21:02.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.32,0:21:11.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, that was an internal phone, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.50,0:21:17.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Dad seriously still believes the police are on their way?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.88,0:21:19.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's find a phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:25.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.76,0:21:28.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.21,0:21:32.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We need to call the police quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.96,0:21:36.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought Mibu had already done so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.26,0:21:39.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was just pretending.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.73,0:21:43.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}, run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.98,0:21:49.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't move, Missy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.91,0:21:58.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...so I said, aren't you gonna drink the whole thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.96,0:22:08.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You didn't imagine that the three of us were working together, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.67,0:22:11.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait here until we've dealt with the curator.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.25,0:22:14.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then that Nagata guy's in on it too?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.75,0:22:15.82,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.59,0:22:19.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Curator Izumi's in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.00,0:23:45.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.15,0:23:47.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Too bad, you were so close.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.45,0:23:58.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the next Conan: 'Demons Dance at Noh Mask Mansion (Part II)'!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.45,0:24:03.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Chisel!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.46,0:24:05.21,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I heard there'll be some info about the movie today.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.21,0:24:06.69,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,What? Lupin vs. Kogorō, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.69,0:24:08.00,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It's Lupin vs. Conan.
